**  ER (ERROR-MESSAGE)
E-01 NO FINAL SETTING NUMBER ENTRY
E-02 RECEIVER OF BILL IS 0111
E-03 NO K-TYPE(S) ENTRY
E-04 NO ENTRY IN REVERSING DEPATMENT TYPE
E-05 NO SETTING CODE ENTRY
E-06 SETTING CODE MUST BE NUMERICAL
E-07 NO USER'S NUM,OF DEL. ENTRY
E-08 USER'S NUM.OF DEL.MUST BE EQUAL TO OR UNDER. OF BUS.DAY
E-09 K-TYPE(S) A; USER'S NUM. OF DEL. MUST BE 5 OR OVER 5
E-10 K-TYPE(S) B; USER'S NUM. OF DEL. MUST B 4 OR UNDER 4
E-11 NO BOX TYPE-1 ENTRY
E-12 NO BOX TYPE-2 ENTRY
E-13 NO QUANTITY IN CONTAINER ENTRY
E-14 NO QUANTITY IN CONTAINER UNIT ENTRY
E-15 WRONG DRAWING SECT.
E-16 WRONG SORTING SECT.
E-17 NUMBER OF KANBAN'S MUST BE EQUAL TO OR UNDER 90000
E-18 OBSOLETE KANBAN DATA,REMAKE REQUIRED
E-19 WRONG LOCATION
E-20 NO DATA IN K-TYPE M/F
E-21 NO VENDOR SECT. IN BAR CODE M/F.
E-22 NO DATA IN DEPARTMENTAL LT M/F
E-23 NO DATA IN SETTING M/F
E-24 NO DATA IN CONDITION M/F
E-25 DUPLICATION OCCURRED IN REVERSING CONDITIION CODE
E-26 WRONG NUMBER OF BOXES ENTRY
E-27 EACH AOYAMA FACTORY IS RECEIVING FACTORY
E-28 ENTER RECEIVING POINT
E-29 NUMBER REQUIRED ALONG WITH COMPONENT PART NO.
E-30 COMPONENT PART NO. REQUIRED ALONG WITH NUMBER
E-31 UPDATE EFFECTIVE DATA DUE TO CHANGE IN KANBAN'S DETAILS
E-32 INPUT SAFETY INVENTORY DETAIL.
